text: József Horváth (born 9 June 1947) is a Hungarian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Hungary Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:People from Komárom-Esztergom County
title: József Horváth (equestrian)
